quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  41,30,"Pellet, wi'uЙ“e Й“en: Joomi amen ko Allah, wanaa goЙ—Й—um goo, hooti Й“e tabiti e Й—um, Й“e woЙ—Й—itii haЙ—aaЙ—i Makko Й—in; Malaa'ika'en hino jippoo e maЙ“Й“e tuma Й“e Жҙettitetee, Й“e wi'ana Й“e: wata on hulu maayde e ko hikkori yeeso mayre, wata on sunano ko acciЙ—on aduna; wewliree Aljanna mo wonanoЙ—on e fodeede on aduna, sabu ko gomЙ—inirЙ—on kon Allah, golluЙ—on ko moЖҙЖҙi."
  41,31,"Ko menen woni yiЙ—Й“e mon Й“en ka nguurndam aduna, tawde men semmbinayno on men reena on, ko menen kadi woni yiЙ—Й“e mon Й“en ka laakara: ngol giggol no heddii. Hino woodani on ka Aljanna, kala ko wonkiiji mon faaletee, immorde e dakammeeji e muuyanteeji. Hino woodani on ton kadi, kala ko faaleteЙ—on."
  41,32,"ЖҠum ko maraari helaandi fii hottude mon, immorde e Joomiraawo, Haforoowo junuubi kala tuubanЙ—o Mo e jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, HinnotooЙ—o Й“e."
  41,33,"Alaa Й“urЙ—o moЖҙЖҙude konngol, wano on nodduЙ—o e fii wootinЙ—ingol Allah, o gollitiri sari'a Makko on, o golli golle moЖҙЖҙe weltinayЙ—e Joomi makko, o wi'i: min on, ko e jebbilaniiЙ“e yankinanii Allah Й“en, mi jeyaa? Wa'uЙ—o non fow, ko on Й“uri yimЙ“e Й“en moЖҙЖҙude konngol."
  41,34,"Golle moЖҙЖҙe Й—en e Й—oftaare weltinaynde Allah nden, fotataa e bone maa geddi tikkinayЙ—i Mo Й—in. DuГұir ko Й“uri e moЖҙЖҙude, on boniiЙ—o e maaЙ—a; e jaka yoo, on mo ngayngu woni hakkunde maa e mun, si tawii a duГұirii bone makko on moЖҙЖҙere, himo wa'ita wa giЙ—o saЙ—tuЙ—o giggol."
  41,35,"Hawrataa e on jikku yettiniiЙ—o, si wanaa muГұГұotooЙ“e lorra e bone yimЙ“e Й“en; hawrataa e mun, si wanaa jom geЙ“al manngal. Tawde ko e Й—um moЖҙЖҙere Й—uuЙ—unde woni."
  41,36,"Si seytaane arii sowinsinirde maa bonnugol e kala, waqtu moolor Allah, yiltoЙ—aa e Makko. Ko Kanko woni Nanoowo ko wowlataa kon, AnnduЙ—o fii maaЙ—a."
  41,37,"Hino jeyaa e maandeeji tindinayЙ—i e mawngu Makko ngun, jemma on e Гұalorama on ko waylondirta kon, e naange ngen e lewru ndun. Onon Й“ee yimЙ“e, wata sujjan naange ngen wanaa kadi lewru ndun. Sujjanee Allah tun, taguЙ—o Й—i On, si wonii ko Kanko rewoton."
  41,38,"Si Й“e townitorii Й—uurnagol, Й“e sujjanaali Allah taguЙ—o On, haray Malaa'ika'en wonЙ“e ka Allah Й“en, hiЙ“e subbunhinoo Й“e yetta Mo jemma e Гұalorma, hara Й“e haaЙ“ataa rewugol Mo."